## Output
Reason: one short narrative beat, past tense, grounded in the actual trigger. 80 words max. No abstract reasoning, no compatibility summaries.

If no scene:
{% raw %}
{
  "reason": "Short explanation of why no scene exists right now. 1-2 short sentences.",
  "scene": null
}
{% endraw %}

If a scene exists:
{% raw %}
{
  "reason": "One tight short narrative beat in past tense explaining the immediate trigger. 1-2 short sentences.",
  "scene": {
    "intent": "chosen intent keyword",
    "mainActors": ["Display names"],
    "secondaryActors": ["Display names"],
    "sexualPosition": "position from available list",
    "sexualActivity": "single activity keyword or empty string",
    "furniture": "exact furniture type from available list"
  }
}
{% endraw %}

Return a single raw JSON object. No markdown, no code fences. Must start with { and end with }.
[ end system ]

